---

<div
    class="fixed inset-0 z-[100002] bg-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-center overflow-hidden"
>
    <!-- Decoración de fondo -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none"
    >
        <div
            class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-gold/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-gold/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl animate-in fade-in zoom-in duration-700"
    >
        <div
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-3xl mb-8 border border-brand-gold/20"
        >
            <svg
                class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-gold"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
                ></path>
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Marca Fashion Store -->
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-brand-gold mb-4 opacity-70"
        >
            <span class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-gold/30"></span>
            Fashion Store
            <span class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-gold/30"></span>
        </div>

        <h1
            class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-6 uppercase"
        >
            ESTAMOS EN <br />
            <span class="text-brand-gold italic font-serif normal-case"
                >Mantenimiento</span
            >
        </h1>

        <p
            class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-10 leading-relaxed"
        >
            Estamos trabajando en mejoras exclusivas para tu experiencia.
            Volveremos muy pronto con nuevas colecciones y sorpresas.
        </p>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4"
        >
            <div
                class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-gold animate-pulse"
                ></span>
                <span
                    class="text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300"
                    >Equipo Técnico Activo</span
                >
            </div>
            <a
                href="mailto:soporte@fashionstore.com"
                class="text-brand-gold hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm font-bold underline"
            >
                Contacto de Soporte
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
